[{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0011","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0011.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-0985","title":"Joomla! Abbreviations Manager (com_abbrev) 本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 Abbreviations Manager (com_abbrev) 组件 1.1 版本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在 controller 参数中插入 `../` 序列，绕过路径限制访问并包含服务器上任意本地文件，导致敏感信息泄露或在特定条件下执行任意 PHP 代码。该漏洞利用无需身份认证，仅需目标安装受影响组件即可触发。CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，建议用户立即禁用或升级该组件。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-0985"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-03-16T19:30:00.790","updated":"2026-06-16T23:17:15.667","remediation":"建议立即卸载 Joomla! 的 com_abbrev 组件（Abbreviations Manager v1.1）。若业务必须保留该组件，在 index.php 中对 controller 参数进行白名单校验，仅允许预定义的有效控制器名称（如 array('edit', 'save', 'list')），拒绝包含 .. 或 / 等路径遍历字符的输入。同时确保 PHP 配置中 allow_url_fopen = Off 并设置 open_basedir 限制文件访问范围作为纵深防御。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/61458","http://secunia.com/advisories/37834","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/10948","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/37560","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/55348","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/10948","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0985.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-0985.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0985.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-0985.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2010-0985-1535.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-0985-1538.yaml","https://github.com/rix4uni/nucleihub-templates/blob/579a0234551b9e0e322460a62dc77bd6109e4aff/nucleihub-templates/CVE-2010-0985_3.yaml","https://github.com/gongzeq/VAPT3/blob/3576a7accf5cbadc8e64924d6ff48393db379ea7/secbot/resource/poc/cve/cve-2010-0985-1535.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2010/CVE-2010-0985.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x38000/37560/info.html","https://github.com/Vasileios-Mavroeidis/semantic-stix-vulnerability/blob/30f07606133364b9623f401bc306c8c9cbcf9386/vulnerability/vulnerability--598a2a01-6482-44bb-984c-bcbc63229b67.owl"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0011.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0009","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0009.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-0972","title":"Joomla! GCalendar 组件本地文件包含漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 GCalendar 组件（com_gcalendar）2.1.5 版本存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者无需身份认证即可通过向 index.php 的 controller 参数提交包含 `..`（点点）的恶意路径，实现任意本地文件的包含与执行。该漏洞影响 Joomla! 中使用 com_gcalendar 组件的网站，CVSS 评分 7.5，危害等级高，攻击复杂度低且无需特权。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-0972"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-03-16T19:00:00.727","updated":"2026-06-16T23:17:14.237","remediation":"立即卸载 Joomla! 的 GCalendar Suite 组件（com_gcalendar）2.1.5 及所有更早版本，该扩展已停止维护无补丁可用。如因业务需要暂时保留，可在 Joomla! 全局配置中启用「输入过滤」并将「过滤选项」设为「白名单」以拦截路径遍历 payload，或在 Web 服务器（Apache/Nginx）层面添加规则过滤 controller 参数中的 ../ 序列。建议改用仍在维护的日历扩展替代。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://secunia.com/advisories/38925","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11738","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/56863","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11738","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0972.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-0972.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb