，属于 CWE-22 路径遍历类漏洞，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。受影响版本为 Joomla! 使用 com_jashowcase 组件的相关部署。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-0943"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-03-08T15:30:00.777","updated":"2026-06-16T23:17:11.003","remediation":"该组件发布于 2010 年且已停止维护，不存在官方补丁。建议立即从 Joomla 后台卸载 com_jashowcase 组件，改用其他仍在维护的 Joomla 展示类扩展（如 RSMediaGallery）替代。如无法立即卸载，可在网站根目录 .htaccess 中添加 RewriteRule 拦截 controller 参数中包含 ../ 的请求，或通过 WAF 规则过滤 controller 参数中的目录遍历序列作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1001-exploits/joomlajashowcase-traversal.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/33486","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11090","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/37692","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/55512","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11090","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0943.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-0943.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0943.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-0943.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5001-to-6000-templates/cve-2010-0943-1516.yaml","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/2010/CVE-2010-0943.json","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-0943_18.yaml","https://github.com/patrickmpalmer/exploit-prediction-calculator/blob/a048424e68e6b5ea7f4d32bf29dddd4eda342b01/data_gathering/data/exploited_cves.csv","https://github.com/0xelixer/new/blob/6f6dd4a43a76ce74c1e8cc0558629a2ea198286e/nuclei-temps/Vulnerability-Templates/template2/cve-2010-0943-1517.yaml","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-reports/blob/3e2a1bd3dbca1b431f18ed0dabb71fa729d4d059/2022/Nov/13/Artifact/Report.csv","https://github.com/justakazh/CVE_Database/blob/06bd07f32c89b43f30d59ff450dfbb661e471cbe/2010/CVE-2010-0943.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0007.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0008","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0008.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-0944","title":"Joomla! JCollection 组件目录遍历漏洞","description":"Joomla! 的 JCollection 组件（com_jcollection）存在目录遍历漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 index.php 的 controller 参数传递 `../` 序列，绕过路径限制读取服务器上任意敏感文件（如配置文件、数据库凭据等）。该漏洞影响 Joomla! 中使用 com_jcollection 组件的版本，攻击无需身份认证，利用难度低。建议用户升级至官方修复版本或卸载受影响组件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-0944"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-03-08T15:30:00.810","updated":"2026-06-16T23:17:11.117","remediation":"卸载 com_jcollection 组件或通过 Joomla 扩展管理器禁用该组件。如必须使用，在网站根目录 .htaccess 中添加规则阻止对 index.php 的 controller 参数传递目录遍历序列（如 `..%2f`），或部署 WAF 规则拦截路径遍历攻击载荷。升级 Joomla 核心至 2.5 以上版本也可降低风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1001-exploits/joomlajcollection-traversal.txt","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11088","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/37691","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/55514","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11088","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0944.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-0944.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0944.yaml","https://github.com/sepehrdaddev/zap-scripts/blob/2b63b02ca79cc7f0023cdbab72c5c6c774354b07/active/CVE-2010-0944.js","https://github.com/0xKayala/Custom-Nuclei-Templates/blob/1940dfd29577590f076c89dec5c30d809d68f210/5