/secunia.com/advisories/38637","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11498","http://www.osvdb.org/62486","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/38296","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/56380","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0759.yaml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/2010/POC-AVE-2010-0005.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/2010/AVE-2010-0005.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-2010-0004","file_name":"2010/AVE-2010-0004.toml","cve_id":"CVE-2010-0696","title":"JoomlaWorks AllVideos Joomla 插件目录遍历漏洞","description":"JoomlaWorks 开发的 Joomla! 组件 AllVideos (Jw_allVideos) 3.0 至 3.2 版本中的 includes/download.php 存在目录遍历漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向 file 参数传递经过特殊构造的 `./../.../` 序列绕过路径限制，实现任意文件读取。该漏洞允许未授权攻击者读取服务器上任意敏感文件（如配置文件、数据库凭据等），危害较大。CVSS 评分 5.0，属于中危漏洞，建议用户立即升级或停用受影响组件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-0696"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-02-23T18:30:00.717","updated":"2026-06-16T23:16:40.280","remediation":"升级 JoomlaWorks AllVideos 插件至 3.3 及以上版本，或在 Joomla 后台卸载该插件并更换为官方维护的替代插件。若无升级条件，可删除 `includes/download.php` 文件中的 `file` 参数处理逻辑，或在 Web 服务器层（如 .htaccess）限制 `download.php` 的直接访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://osvdb.org/62331","http://secunia.com/advisories/38587","http://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11447","http://www.joomlaworks.gr/content/view/77/34/","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/38238","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/11447","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0696.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-0696.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0696.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb903