 参数注入 .. (点点) 路径遍历序列，包含并执行服务器上的任意本地文件。该漏洞属于本地文件包含 (LFI) 类型，无需身份认证即可远程利用，CVSS 评分 7.5 (HIGH)，影响使用该组件的所有 Joomla! 站点。攻击者可读取敏感系统文件 (如 /etc/passwd)、配置文件或包含恶意脚本实现代码执行。厂商已停止维护该组件，建议迁移至替代组件或升级至安全版本。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-2010-0157"],"sources":["nuclei"],"published":"2010-01-06T22:00:12.450","updated":"2026-06-16T23:15:35.200","remediation":"立即卸载 com_biblestudy 组件（版本 6.1 及以下均受影响）。如业务必须使用，请升级到已修复此目录遍历漏洞的最新版本；若开发者已不再维护，则彻底移除该组件。作为临时缓解措施，可在 Web 服务器或 WAF 层面拦截 URL 中 controller 参数包含 \"../\" 的请求，或编辑 Joomla 配置文件加入 `$controller = preg_replace('/[^A-Za-z0-9]/', '', $controller);` 进行输入过滤。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-15T00:00:00Z","references":["http://packetstormsecurity.org/1001-exploits/joomlabiblestudy-lfi.txt","http://secunia.com/advisories/37896","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/37583","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/10943","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/main/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0157.yaml","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/a90de4f84b4783951362f491671e1e9decfc17cb/2010/CVE-2010-0157.md","https://github.com/projectdiscovery/nuclei-templates/blob/1482f62c613998b0fe0690591034b732c0bb2e0a/http/cves/2010/CVE-2010-0157.yaml","https://github.com/ExpLangcn/NucleiTP/blob/2b7ecb9031a6eda4f272793045f29b339d8e0cce/CVES/high/cve-2010-0157-1486.yaml","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/e61be9425da7cd98fab7bf6d914282e65c9f9042/CVE/data/2010/CVE-2010-0157.json","https://github.com/GhostTroops/scan4all/blob/fff03b51bf79c8993a46c1da766ec993e1102c47/config/51pwn/CVE-2010-0157.yaml","https://github.com/linuxadi/40k-nuclei-templates/blob/542be6820c801c02a33aee60f1c05ca7b0b5005f/aditya/folder1/cve-2010-0157-1485.yaml","https://github.com/adampielak/nuclei-templates/blob/ac9605f5a915670fd80cb4e1904f4435f1835b65/nuclei-v3/C/CVE-2010-0157_21.yaml","https://github.com/ARPSyndicate/suricata-vedas/blob/fe24794ad36564b5bbc7c69101525011387b8650/2010/CVE-2010-0157.rules","https://github.com/coreruleset/seaweed-repor